title: Rihanna-Shut up and drive, by ErikB.NL
description:
Rihanna Shut up and Drive!

Soundtrack |  Actress |  Producer 

Robyn Rihanna Fenty
was born in a parish in Barbados called St. Michael,
to Monica (Braithwaite), an accountant,
and Ronald Fenty, a warehouse supervisor.
Her mother is of Afro-Guyanese descent
and her father has Afro-Barbadian and English/Irish/Scottish ancestry
(known as "Redlegs" in the Caribbean).
Rihanna lived the life of a normal island girl.  

Born:  Robyn Rihanna Fenty  
February 20, 1988  in St. Michael, Barbados
